'''Club Belgrano de San Nicolás''' is a professional [[basketball]] team in [[San Nicolás de los Arroyos]], [[Argentina]] playing in the [[Liga Nacional de Básquetbol]] (LNB). Their home arena is [[Fortunato Bonelli Arena]].

