{{Infobox stadium | stadium_name = L'Àgora | image = Ágora, Ciudad de las Artes y las Ciencias, Valencia, España, 2014-06-29, DD 44.JPG | location = [[Valencia, Spain]] | coordinates = | broke_ground = | opened = 2009 <ref>{{cite web|last1=Mallorca|first1=Diario de|title=¿El arquitecto que no sabía diseñar velódromos? - Diario de Mallorca|url=http://www.diariodemallorca.es/mallorca/2009/08/09/arquitecto-sabia-disenar-velodromos/492223.html|website=www.diariodemallorca.es|accessdate=5 May 2016}}</ref> | closed = | demolished = | owner = | operator = | construction_cost = [[Euro|€]] 90 million | architect = [[Santiago Calatrava]] | former_names = | tenants = [[Valencia Open 500]] | seating_capacity = 6,075 }}
'''L'Àgora''' ({{IPA-ca|ˈlaɣoɾa|langva}}, {{IPA-ca|ˈlaɣuɾə|ec}}; {{lang-es|El Ágora}}, "The Agora") is a multifunctional covered space designed by [[Santiago Calatrava]] located in the ''[[City of Arts and Sciences|Ciutat de les Arts i les Ciències]]'' (City of Arts and Sciences) complex, [[Valencia, Spain]]. The building has a height of 80&nbsp;m and occupies 5,000&nbsp;m<sup>2</sup> of [[elliptic]] space. Depending on the configuration of the space, a maximum [[seating capacity]] for 6,075 people can be reached.<ref>{{cite web|last1=S.L.|first1=Unidad Editorial Internet,|title=Así será el Ágora de Valencia {{!}} elmundo.es|url=http://www.elmundo.es/elmundo/2009/01/05/valencia/1231148187.html|website=www.elmundo.es|accessdate=5 May 2016}}</ref>
L'Àgora was officially inaugurated in November 2009 to host the [[Valencia Open 500]] [[Association of Tennis Professionals|ATP]] tournament, although the construction works were not completely finished.<ref>http://www.lavanguardia.es/free/edicionimpresa/res/20091106/53818490214.html?urlback=http://www.lavanguardia.es/premium/edicionimpresa/20091106/53818490214.html</ref>
[[File:Agora and El Puente de l'Assut de l'Or Bridge.jpg|thumb|right|[[Assut de l'Or Bridge]] and the L'Àgora are two parts of Valencia's City of Arts and Sciences complex]] [[File:Kohlschreiber-Mayer vs Isner-Lopez VLC - 60.jpeg|left|thumb|L'Àgora, with the tennis configuration.]]
