'''Malawi Cricket Union''' is the official [[Sport governing body|governing body]] of the sport of [[cricket]] in [[Malawi]]. Its current headquarters is in [[Blantyre, Malawi]]. Malawi Cricket Union is Malawi's representative at the [[International Cricket Council]] and is an affiliate member and has been a member of that body since 1998. It is also a member of the [[African Cricket Association]]. 

