{{Infobox stadium | stadium_name = Sakon Nakhon City municipality Stadium | image = | location = [[Sakon Nakhon province|Sakon Nakhon]], [[Thailand]] | coordinates = {{coord|17.146115|104.156992|format=dms|type:landmark_scale:3000}} | opened = | owner = | operator = | surface = [[Grass]] | construction_cost = | former_names = | tenants = [[Sakon Nakhon F.C.]] 2010-2011 | seating_capacity = 1,514 }}
'''Sakon Nakhon City municipality Stadium''' ({{lang-th|สนามกีฬาเทศบาลนครสกลนคร}}) is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Sakon Nakhon Province]], [[Thailand]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of [[Sakon Nakhon F.C.]]
